data.title: Glow Digital Art Sticker

user.description:
OpticalArtInc. is an art project that was launched in 2009. The initial works consisted of simple forms of Sacred Geometry, which were then fertilized by the influence of Op Art. This is how the first Op-Art works by OpticalArtInc came about. This was expressed in static works of art, as pictures for the wall or as design pieces of furniture, but it shouldn't stop there. We set out to give Op-Art a different form of representation by bringing this art direction into three-dimensional space, thus creating the series of “Plastiques”, “Kaleidoskopic” and, ultimately, the idea of making Op Art movable. "Op-Art in Motion" was now the new creative area, from which the street art project "Illu my Nation" emerged in 2019, a representation of art in public space, it is what it is, immaterial and in the next moment already extinguished and in another Place.
OpticalArtInc. is the heart of our creative field and with heart, hand and brain we try to integrate art into everyday life.
